QUALIFIER.NAME: Description
QUALIFIER.VALUE: The Spared association indicates an element that is acting as a replacement for another element. If the Dependent references a Collection, this indicates that 'spared' element is a member of that collection and the actual mapping between the spare and the spared is un-important.

QUALIFIER.NAME: Description
QUALIFIER.VALUE: A ManagedElement that has replaced/spared another the reference Dependent element.

QUALIFIER.NAME: Description
QUALIFIER.VALUE: The Element or Elements (in the case of a collection) that have been replaced/spared.
